"        'claim load that the in-silico axes cannot bound).',\n" +
"        'unplaced_precedent_in_repo': 'AXIS/HIERARCHY.tape '\n" +
"        '@N genetic_medicine_status + @N adc_status \\u2014 same CBER-scope '\n" +
"        'UNPLACED handling already established (Zolgensma / Casgevy / '\n" +
"        'Comirnaty for gene/cell/mRNA; Enhertu / Kadcyla for ADCs). '\n" +
"        'Anti-amyloid mAbs join the same honesty cohort.',\n" +
"        'drug_precedent_citations': [\n" +
"            'van Dyck CH et al. 2023, N Engl J Med 388:9-21 '\n" +
"            '(CLARITY AD lecanemab phase-3)',\n" +
"            'FDA STN BL 761269 \\u2014 lecanemab-irmb (Leqembi) '\n" +
"            'accelerated approval 2023-01-06; traditional approval '\n" +
"            '2023-07-06, CBER',\n" +
